{
  "stem": "26609.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, as I walked around, behind, there were always some Ukrainians-- these were the worst, except a few good people, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were behind me-- walking, always, behind me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe because it's a Ukrainian girl, maybe a-- some men behind me, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- I just went out of their way, all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they talked to me, I didn't even answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was better not to answer than to answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And once, as I stood there, suddenly I had a look-- just before my eyes-- a woman-- that what I want to tell you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A woman with a daughter-- a middle-aged woman, and a young daughter, I don't know, maybe 18, 20.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were both dressed in black, and hats-- very elegant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some people, I found out later, came from Warsaw to Lwow-- travelled when-- not as Jews, in mourning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's why they were all in black.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They disguised themself, that they are in mourning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A woman-- very elegant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And had two cases.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She carried the big case.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'll never forget that picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She carried the big case, and her daughter carried a case.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And because they were different than other people, they stood out of the crowd.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "As to-- go to-- How they got there, I don't know-- to-- sent to forced labor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it was silly to dress like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They thought they dress-- they disguise themself, and no one will suspect anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But, because they stood out of the crowd-- I was dressed as a poor Ukrainian girl, not that-- old clothes, just not new clothes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But these were dressed very elegant, in mourning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And a Gestapo man came up to them and asked them to open the case.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
